---
alwaysApply: true
---
- Use pytest and pytest-cov for all tests
- The test suite must maintain at least 80% coverage
- Each router must include at least 5 test cases, covering:
    - Success scenarios
    - Error scenarios
    - Edge cases
- Tests must not depend on real BigQuery or MongoDB connections—only stubbed data
- Tests must use FastAPI’s TestClient or httpx
- When implementing new endpoints or features, generate the corresponding tests in the same MR
